Ask HN: Looking for a mentor as I move from dev to dev manager
text:
I’ve been a developer for 20+ years. I’m moving into more of a managing role and I feel like im struggling to lead my team well.

I’ve read a few books and work to apply them but I think my biggest issue is letting go and trusting others.

Anyone else have this issue? How did you overcome it?

Would anyone be willing to mentor me?
